{"tid":921780,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"﻿聖誕禮遇  買白色 Galaxy Note9，送國泰來回大阪機票！","createTime":"2018-11-29T23:59:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T11:40:06.000Z","uid":141060,"like":7,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"6cafa2bf8bdb3f0012094606d34c57d70401dbf4","tid":921780,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T23:59:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.mobilemagazinehk.com/2018/11/%E8%B2%B7%E7%99%BD%E8%89%B2-galaxy-note9%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%81%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E4%BE%86%E5%9B%9E%E5%A4%A7%E9%98%AA%E6%A9%9F%E7%A5%A8%EF%BC%81.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mobilemagazinehk.com%2F2018%2F11%2F%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E7%2599%25BD%25E8%2589%25B2-galaxy-note9%25EF%25BC%258C%25E9%2580%2581%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E4%25BE%2586%25E5%259B%259E%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2598%25AA%25E6%25A9%259F%25E7%25A5%25A8%25EF%25BC%2581.html&d=%2FWF5AIj6jbqjK091Au4%2FB9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=0040716b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mobilemagazinehk.com/2018/11/%E8%B2%B7%E7%99%BD%E8%89%B2-galaxy-note9%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%81%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E4%BE%86%E5%9B%9E%E5%A4%A7%E9%98%AA%E6%A9%9F%E7%A5%A8%EF%BC%81.html</a><br />\n<br />\n白色 Galaxy Note9，送國泰來回大阪機票！<br />\nSamsung 香港今天宣布推出Galaxy Note9白色版本，並於12月7日正式上市，並提供 128GB 及 512GB 兩個版本。此外，Samsung 香港更於2018年12月1日至12月31日期間推出Samsung聖誕禮遇優惠，凡購買 Galaxy Note9 的用戶更有機會獲大阪來回機票或Samsung Pay八達通（Smart Octopus）增值額獎賞。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mobilemagazinehk.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/IMG_20181129_145447.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mobilemagazinehk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2FIMG_20181129_145447.jpg&h=0281f898&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n次白色版本 Galaxy Note9 除了顏色不同外，其他規格上都與其他顏色的 Galaxy Note9 相同，同是採用6.4吋19.5:9比例屏幕，配備 Snapdragon 845 處理器，內建6GB + 128GB 及 8GB + 256GB 兩個版本，搭載1200 + 1200萬像雙鏡頭及800萬像自拍鏡頭，電池容量為 4000mAh等。<br />\n￼<br />\n另外，Samsung於12月1日至12月31日推出聖誕禮遇優惠期，今次聖誕優惠的產品除了有Galaxy Note9 外，還有Galaxy Watch、Galaxy A系列、Galaxy Tab S4、Notebook 9 Pen及 Notebook Flash等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mobilemagazinehk.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/IMG_20181129_153114.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mobilemagazinehk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2FIMG_20181129_153114.jpg&h=53a0f75c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56e01fcc23aee78656be75aa2280b38325c00e6b","tid":921780,"uid":151333,"like":6,"dislike":68,"score":-62,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T00:48:41.000Z","msg":"送泰國來回日本機票對我地香港人有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1401739cef7ea33f5903e6616eaecec8bd0d6c9","tid":921780,"uid":1067,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"56e01fcc23aee78656be75aa2280b38325c00e6b","tid":921780,"uid":151333,"like":6,"dislike":68,"score":-62,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T00:48:41.000Z","msg":"送泰國來回日本機票對我地香港人有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T00:52:19.000Z","msg":"國泰來回大阪"},{"pid":"d24e9e1ebd5c8fbb699c5968c163cbbaedf849ad","tid":921780,"uid":158977,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T01:06:51.000Z","msg":"機票有效期為2至7天<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55224dce33cc8c025a9947cc3d8ade71a823a198","tid":921780,"uid":141060,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"56e01fcc23aee78656be75aa2280b38325c00e6b","tid":921780,"uid":151333,"like":6,"dislike":68,"score":-62,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T00:48:41.000Z","msg":"送泰國來回日本機票對我地香港人有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T01:11:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkg